    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hitmen Havoc：策略与混乱的狂野结合</h2><br><strong>Hitmen Havoc是一款卡通风格、快节奏的2D竞技场派对射击游戏，在这里，策略与混乱交织在一起。无论你是与朋友、敌人、陌生人还是观众对战，每一场比赛都是一次新的、令人兴奋的挑战。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从8个独特的角色中选择，每个角色都有自己特殊的技能和属性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/f20dc063b7004de13ec8c0ee5d47d7d9.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/f20dc063b7004de13ec8c0ee5d47d7d9.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/f20dc063b7004de13ec8c0ee5d47d7d9.mp4?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>投入到可自定义的游戏模式中，让每一次行动都充满不可预知性和刺激感。 <br>无论是快速游戏还是热闹的派对，Hitmen Havoc都能在每一轮比赛中带来难忘的竞技乐趣。<br><br>多样化的武器库：装备多种武器，每一种武器都为混乱的游戏增添了独特的风味。从精准射击到爆炸性混乱，应有尽有，适合各种场景。<br>动态竞技场：在多个关卡中战斗，每个关卡都提供独特的环境和挑战，时刻让你保持警觉。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/91f38b4296d0758583ceb9921c1f47ac.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/91f38b4296d0758583ceb9921c1f47ac.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/91f38b4296d0758583ceb9921c1f47ac.mp4?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器展示</h2><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/e115868fde153f9e3d7c8c85a0663c26.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/e115868fde153f9e3d7c8c85a0663c26.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>手枪：</strong>你忠实的伙伴！虽然时刻陪伴，但别指望奇迹。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/c311b28fdefa0537160b8780aa797fc3.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/c311b28fdefa0537160b8780aa797fc3.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>冲锋枪：</strong>疯狂扫射！倾泻子弹雨，看着混乱肆虐。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/8d210704f2e6524dd7d7bce0defa676c.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/8d210704f2e6524dd7d7bce0defa676c.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>突击步枪：</strong>全能型武器！稳定的射击适合每一场复仇。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/2e4a08afd93da0b0a273a29ecfba5ab2.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/2e4a08afd93da0b0a273a29ecfba5ab2.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>激光爆能枪：</strong>嗞嗞嗞，轰隆！蓄力射击，震慑对手！</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/058951951dcbab800ad6ff7a039c013c.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/058951951dcbab800ad6ff7a039c013c.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>弩：</strong>双重威胁！击退与伤害，双重打击！</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/4d159fec92cf1a05afdbf6cfbc95bea1.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/4d159fec92cf1a05afdbf6cfbc95bea1.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>狙击步枪：</strong>排好队！一发致命，穿透多个敌人。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/aaffc23187c3848cdf238f92ba16aa3a.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/aaffc23187c3848cdf238f92ba16aa3a.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>拳击：</strong>愤怒之拳！一拳将敌人打飞到另一个世界。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/1c2df0a730db9090728a633ed127224b.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/1c2df0a730db9090728a633ed127224b.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>能量手榴弹：</strong>远程投掷，强力打击！蓄力后投掷更远，享受爆炸乐趣。</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/a0333dce61246cc5473b793593f6762a.poster.avif?t=1727440778\" width=150 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137300/extras/a0333dce61246cc5473b793593f6762a.webm?t=1727440778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></td><td><strong>火箭筒：</strong>巨大的混乱！强力打击，但注意弹药。</td></tr></table><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家评价</h2><br><blockquote> &quot;和朋友们在线玩Hitmen Havoc时玩得非常开心。我们在比赛中的一些疯狂时刻让我们笑得停不下来。&quot; </blockquote><br><blockquote> &quot;我通常不太喜欢多人游戏，但这个游戏让我上瘾了。尤其是和朋友一起玩时，真的很有趣。&quot; </blockquote><br><blockquote> &quot;比赛很快，但总是让你想再玩一局。这是一天结束后放松的好游戏。&quot; </blockquote><br><blockquote> &quot;这个游戏立刻成为我们小组的最爱。我们经历了一些史诗般的战斗，笑声不断。&quot; </blockquote><br><blockquote> &quot;完全上瘾。我们一直说'再来一局'，结果一晃眼就过去了好几个小时。&quot; </blockquote>",
